		<h2>Contest, surveys and giveaways:</h2>
		<p>While the activities’ details provided by you through the HappyYou by Kotak app would be rewarded as per the eligibility and applicable rewards criteria as decided from time-to-time, Kotak Life may offer you the opportunity to participate in contests, giveaways and other promotions. Any information submitted in connection with such activities will be treated in accordance with this Policy, unless specifically set forth in the terms and conditions/ rules of those contests, giveaways or promotions. From time-to-time, Kotak Life may also ask you to participate in surveys designed to help us improve the HappyYou by Kotak app.</p>
		<h2>Disclaimer for products/ provision of services:</h2>
		<p>While using the HappyYou by Kotak app and consequently availing the products/ services made available to you thereunder; you are advised/ informed that all such products/ services are being provided by third party service providers and you are availing the same at your own risk/ volition. Kotak Life disclaims any and all liability arising out of/ related to such products/ services in any manner whatsoever in nature.</p>
		<h2>Authorization to contact:</h2>
		<p>You authorize Kotak Life to contact you through means such as (i) call; (ii) short messaging service (SMS); (iii) email; (iv) other similar means using the contact information (made available by you on our HappyYou by Kotak app either at the time of subscription/ making an inquiry/ application for any of the offerings provided or otherwise). You agree to receive offer communications from us for the offerings you have opted for and/ or with regards to our other offerings which we feel you may be interested in. You authorize us to contact you by way of any other similar means for the mentioned purpose; irrespective of you being registered with the National Do Not Call (NDNC) registry for a period of 30 (thirty) days from you furnishing the information or not.</p>
		<h2>Data Security:</h2>
		<p>We intend to use a combination of firewall barriers, encryption techniques and authentication procedures among others to maintain the security of your data and to protect Kotak Life’s User Accounts, systems from unauthorized access.</p>
		<p>While Kotak Life has taken reasonable measures to protect your Personal Information/ other information in accordance with this Policy; the internet as such cannot be guaranteed to be completely secure and safe. Kotak Life hence does not warrant the security of any Personal Information/ information provided by you.</p>
		<p>It is important to understand that these precautions only apply to our HappyYou by Kotak app. We exercise no control over how your information is stored, maintained or displayed by third parties or on third party sites.</p>
		<h2>Registration and password:</h2>
		<p>When you register for the HappyYou by Kotak app, Kotak Life shall seek a one-time password (“OTP”) from you for your privacy and security. The said OTP shall be shared with you on the mobile number registered with Kotak Life. This OTP is stored in an encrypted manner on our systems.</p>
		<p>You shall be solely responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login information and OTP. You shall also be responsible for all uses of your login information, whether or not authorized by you. You agree to immediately notify us of any unauthorized use of your login information/ password/ User Account. Kotak Life cannot and does not assume any responsibility or liability for any information submitted by another person who has fraudulently accessed your User Account or any third party's fraudulent use/ misuse of your login information/ password/ your User Account.</p>
		<p>You represent and warrant that the information that you provide about yourself; as requested in the HappyYou by Kotak app is accurate and complete. You agree to update your information as necessary; including providing Kotak Life your current email address and mobile number, so that you may receive timely notifications and other account related communications.</p>
		<h2>Amendments to the Policy:</h2>
		<p>Kotak Life reserves the right to update/ amend/ replace this Policy at any time without any notice and your continued use of your User Account shall be deemed to be your consent to such updated/ amended/ replaced Policy.</p>
